{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c9b25676dd","title":"关于中央一级不准备审判中小贪污犯复习仲勋电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6f99234313","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":15,"articleId":"c9b25676dd"}],"tags":[{"id":"bbc75a90b7","name":"习仲勋","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"b7596446e9","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c9b25676dd","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"习仲勋，当时任中共中央西北局第二书记。"},{"id":"dba3c682fc","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c9b25676dd","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指习仲勋1952年2月13日关于建议中央推迟召开原拟于2月16日召开的公审资污犯（包括若干情节严重的中小贪污犯）大会给毛泽东的电报。"}],"contents":[{"id":"68427c98aa","type":"title","text":"关于中央一级不准备审判中小资污犯复习仲勋电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c9b25676dd"},{"id":"b7596446e9","type":"paragraph","text":"仲勋同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c9b25676dd"},{"id":"dba3c682fc","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十三日电收到。（一）中央一级不准备对中小贪污犯举行审判：（二）西北大行政区准备在二月审判一批资污犯是好的，应选择一亿元以上的大贪污犯，暂时不要审判一亿元以下的。并请先以量刑要点电告。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c9b25676dd"},{"id":"cac0fe1d38","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c9b25676dd"},{"id":"c80a710323","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c9b25676dd"}],"page":{"id":"8f1f70b4fc","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"c9b25676dd","start":400,"end":400}}}},"__N_SSG":true}